text: Aleksandra Zabrocka (born 27 June 1984) is a cyclo cross rider and road cyclist from Poland. She represented her nation at the 2004 UCI Road World Championships. ==References== ==External links== * profile at Procyclingstats.com Category:1984 births Category:Polish female cyclists Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
